Uses of Package
frame

  • Packages that use frame 
    Package Description
    frame
    This package contains everything that works with rendering and processing of resources to the screen, as well as the screen itself.
  • Classes in frame used by frame 
    Class and Description
    GameGraphics
    GameGraphics merges all the maps used into the game into one location, which allows interaction to be done between the player and the terrain.
    GameMouse
    The GameMouse class is used to provide interaction with the mouse, without creating unnecessary clutter in the GamePanel class.
    GamePanel.Button
    Button is the recreation of a JButton made to fit the needs of GamePanel.
    GamePanel.MuteButton
    MuteButton is a special GamePanel.Button that is instantiated once in GamePanel, which allows the user to turn music on and off.
